quran[8{c,v,t}:
6,158,"kya ab log is ke muntazir hain ke un ke samnay farishtay aa kharray hon, ya tumhara rab khud aa jaye, ya tumahray rab ki baaz Sarih nishanain namodaar ho jayen? jis roz tumahray rab ki baaz makhsoos nishanain namodaar ho jayen gi phir kisi aisay shakhs ko is ka imaan kuch faida nah day ga jo pehlay imaan nah laya ho ya jis ne apne imaan mein koi bhalai nah kamaai ho ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! un se keh do ke acha, tum intzaar karo, hum bhi intzaar karte hain"
6,159,"jin logon ne apne deen ko tukre tukre kar diya aur giroh giroh ban gay yaqeenan un se tumhara kuch vaastaa nahi, un ka maamla to Allah ke supurd hai, wohi un ko betaye ga ke unhon ne kya kuch kya hai"
6,160,"jo Allah ke huzoor neki le kar aeye ga is ke liye das gina ajar hai, aur jo badi le kar aeye ga is ko itna hi badla diya jaye ga jitna is ne qasoor kya hai, aur kisi par zulm nah kya jaye ga"
6,161,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! kaho mere rab ne bilyaqeen mujhe seedha rasta dikha diya hai, bilkul theek deen jis mein koi theerh nahi, ibrahim ka tareeqa jisay yaksu ho kar uss ne ikhtiyar kya tha aur woh mushrikon mein se nah tha"
6,162,"kaho, meri namaz, mere tamam marasim abodit, mera jeena aur mera marna, sab kuch Allah rab alaalmin ke liye hai"
6,163,jis ka koi shareek nahi isi ka mujhe hukum diya gaya hai aur sab se pehlay sir itaat jhukanay wala mein hon
6,164,"kaho, kya mein Allah ke siwa koi aur rab talaash karoon halan ke wohi har cheez ka rab hai? har shakhs jo kuch kamata hai is ka zimma daar woh khud hai, koi boojh uthany wala dosray ka boojh nahi uthata, phir tum sab ko apne rab ki taraf palatna hai, uss waqt woh tumahray ikhtilafat ki haqeeqat tum par khol day ga"
6,165,"wohi hai jis ne tum ko zameen ka khalifa banaya, aur tum mein se baaz ko baaz ke muqaabla mein ziyada buland darjay diye, taakay jo kuch tum ko diya hai isi mein tumhari azmaish kere be shak tumhara rab saza dainay mein bhi bohat taiz hai aur bohat dar guzar karne aur reham frmane wala bhi hai"
